org.qscript

Class Result

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.qscript.Result

  • public class Result
extends Object
    A Result object is created when an expression or algorithm has been evaluated.
    To be safe when using the result it is best to see if it is valid with the isValid() method.
    Author:
    Peter Lager
